@startuml
start
:The user opens the file browser;
if (Does the user want to use GUI) then (Yes)
:The user searches for the parent folder;
:The user opens the context menu on the parent folder;
:The user selects "Add file";
:The system displays a dialog for the new name;
if (Does the user want to proceed) then (Yes)
:The user enters the name and submits the dialog;
:The system creates the file;
:The system shows the new file among the parent's neighbors;
else (No)
:The user cancels the operation;
endif
else (No)
:The user issues the DSL command to create the file;
endif
stop
@enduml
